title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Child grows into sweater.” [From a headline in the New York Daily News, 30 November 1982. Submitted by Bernard Witlieb, White Plains, New York, who comments, “Perhaps his bones began to knit.”]
